Dan hari ini...

737
00:45:26,649 --> 00:45:27,942
Ya ampun.

738
00:45:27,942 --> 00:45:30,336
Hai, saya di sini.

739
00:45:30,336 --> 00:45:32,029
Jika Anda tidak suka anjing...

740
00:45:32,029 --> 00:45:33,489
Tidak, tidak sama sekali.

741
00:45:33,489 --> 00:45:35,822
Masuk, masuk.

742
00:45:36,784 --> 00:45:38,936
