755
00:46:18,367 --> 00:46:20,828
Dia bahkan lebih cantik secara pribadi.

756
00:46:20,828 --> 00:46:22,647
Imut-imut sekali.

757
00:46:22,647 --> 00:46:25,567
Dia memang benar.

758
00:46:26,292 --> 00:46:29,218
Tunggu.

759
00:46:29,218 --> 00:46:32,256
Coco, bulumu lembut sekali.

760
00:46:32,256 --> 00:46:34,782
